      <section eId="sec_CCP-1031">
        <num>CCP 1031</num>
        <heading>Section </heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-1031__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>A demand incidental to the principal demand may be instituted against an adverse party, a co-party, or against a third person.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-1031__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Incidental demands are reconvention, cross-claims, intervention, and the demand against third parties.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=111111</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
